<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">　　《相應部》中《緣起相應經》</span><a href="#_ftn8" name="_ftnref8" title="" id="_ftnref8"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%">[8]</span></span></span></a><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">說：「無明緣行，行緣（結生）識</span><a href="#_ftn9" name="_ftnref9" title="" id="_ftnref9"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size:16.0pt;line-height:107%">[9]</span></span></span></a><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">，識緣名色，名色緣六入，六入緣觸，觸緣受，受緣愛，愛緣取，取緣有，有緣生，生緣老、死、愁、悲、苦、憂、惱。」</span></p>

