<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref8" name="_ftn8" title="" id="_ftn8"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%">[8]</span></span></span></a><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">《相應部·因緣相應</span>1<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">經》</span></p>
