<div id="ftn9">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref9" name="_ftn9" title="" id="_ftn9"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%">[9]</span></span></span></a> <span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">英文版用的是</span>rebirth-linking consciousness<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">，就是結生識，現在是按照經文的意譯。巴利文直譯一般是「行緣識」。</span></p>
</div>

<div id="ftn10">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref10" name="_ftn10" title="" id="_ftn10"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%">[10]</span></span></span></a><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">《相應部·蘊相應</span>22<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">經》</span></p>
