<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref11" name="_ftn11" title="" id="_ftn11"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%;
font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif">[11]</span></span></span></span></a><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">這裡是按照《多聞經》（</span>Sutavantasutta<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">）即《相應部</span>·<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">蘊相應</span> 123<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">經》的回答，指的是聞所成智（或慧）。</span></p>
