<div id="ftn20">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref20" name="_ftn20" title="" id="_ftn20"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%">[20]</span></span></span></a><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">對照英文和巴利文，顯然是意譯而不是直譯。所以英文版的</span>Arising from absorption he contemplates the five aggregates<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">（初禪出，觀五蘊）所說的出定，是根據安止定要出定修觀的意思進行的意譯。</span>.</p>
</div>

