</div>

<div id="ftn27">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref27" name="_ftn27" title="" id="_ftn27"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;line-height:107%">[27]</span></span></span></a> <span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">原註：</span> Literally 「worldly daggers.」 At Vbh.A.501 it is explained as reproach (garahā).</p>

<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">字面意思是「世間的匕首」。在</span>Vbh.A.501<span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-family:細明體" xml:lang="ZH-CN">解釋為責備、呵責、非難</span></p>
